<h4>
  Mary Mother of Sorrows
  <br>
  <small>
    Your own soul a sword shall pierce
  </small>
</h4>

<h4>Prayer</h4>
<p>
  Beloved Mother Mary, <br>
help us to bear our own sufferings with patience and resignation. <br>
Give us the courage to unite it to the suffering of your Son, Jesus. <br>
  <br>
  Amen
</p>

